        ],
        "evidence": [
          "remotion/src/load-config.ts lines 71-111 and viewer/src/tools/video-editor/lib/timeline-data.ts resolveTimelineConfig (lines 136-174) both iterate registry assets, create resolvedRegistry entries, map clips to resolved entries with assetEntry, and return the same ResolvedTimelineConfig shape. The only difference is URL resolution (staticFile vs resolveAssetUrl)."
